      <text>Volume of tetrahedron with vertices i+j+k, i, j, k is:</text>
      <option id="A">1/6 |[a-d, b-d, c-d]| = 1/6</option>
      <option id="B">1/3</option>
      <option id="C">None</option>
      <option id="D">D</option>
      <answer>A</answer>
      <explanation>Vertices (1,1,1), (1,0,0), (0,1,0), (0,0,1). Rel vertices (0,-1,-1), (-1,0,-1), (-1,-1,0). Det = 1(1) + 1(-1) = 0? Wait. (0,-1,-1), (-1,0,-1), (-1,-1,0) -&gt; 0 - (-1)(-1) + (-1)(1) = -1 - 1 = -2. Volume = |-2|/6 = 1/3.</explanation>
    </question>
